nodes.title: KSampler settings
widgets_values:
You can test and find the best setting by yourself. The following table is for reference.
|   | Qwen | Comfy | lightning LoRA |
|--------|---------|------------|---------------------------|
| Steps  | 40      | 20         | 4                         |
| CFG    | 4.0     | 4.0       | 1.0                       |

By default, we use 20 steps as we just don't want it to take too long. Try 40 if you want a better result, but it will take longer.

Subtle recessed LED lighting in the ceiling. Reflection of the moon on the water. High-end luxury, sharp architectural edges, cold blue tones.

nodes.title: LIB: HOME INTERIORS - Steampunk Mechanic's Den
widgets_values: A home interior filled with brass pipes, copper gears, and hissing steam valves. A leather armchair sits next to a glowing coal-powered heater. The room is lit by Edison bulbs and glowing vacuum tubes. Industrial Victorian, intricate clockwork, sepia tones.

nodes.title: LIB: HOME INTERIORS - Traditional Japanese Washroom
widgets_values: A serene bathroom featuring a deep wooden soaking tub (ofuro) made of hinoki wood. Smooth river stones line the floor. A single bamboo sprout drips water into a stone basin. Soft diffused light through frosted glass. Spa-like atmosphere, organic materials, minimalist.

nodes.title: LIB: HOME INTERIORS - Future-Retro 80s Living Room
widgets_values: A neon-lit living room with a sunken conversation pit and geometric patterned wallpaper. A large CRT television plays static. Glass coffee tables and chrome accents. Pink and purple ambient lighting. Synthwave aesthetic, nostalgic, vibrant saturation.

nodes.title: LIB: OFFICE SPACES - Mid-Century Executive Suite

On the heavy desk sits a vintage typewriter, a crystal decanter, and a brass lamp. Warm film grain, cinematic bokeh, Mad Men aesthetic.

nodes.title: LIB: OFFICE SPACES - High-Tech Cyberpunk Workspace
widgets_values: A dark workstation illuminated by neon cyan and magenta light strips. Multiple curved holographic monitors display scrolling code and digital blueprints. Mechanical keyboards with custom keycaps and tangled glowing fiber-optic cables. Industrial hardware, rainy city view through a reinforced window, high contrast.

nodes.title: LIB: OFFICE SPACES - Minimalist Scandinavian Studio
widgets_values: A bright and airy creative studio with white walls and light oak floors. Large industrial windows let in soft diffused daylight. A long trestle table holds a sleek laptop and a single ceramic vase with a monstera leaf. Clean lines, organized clutter, soft shadows, architectural photography style.

nodes.title: LIB: OFFICE SPACES - The Alchemist's Study
widgets_values: A cramped and dusty workspace filled with floor-to-ceiling bookshelves. The desk is covered in yellowed parchment scrolls, bubbling glass retorts, and iron astrolabes. Dozens of melting candles provide a flickering warm amber glow. Magical atmosphere, historical realism, intricate props, dark academia.

nodes.title: LIB: OFFICE SPACES - NASA Mission Control

A massive projection screen on the front wall shows a trajectory map of a spacecraft. Engineers in white short-sleeved shirts work under humming fluorescent lights. Retro-futurism, 1970s technology, grainy CCTV aesthetic.

nodes.title: LIB: OFFICE SPACES - Greenhouse Botany Lab

Sunlight streaks through the glass panes casting leafy shadows on the metal desks. Organic tech, bright lighting, macro botanical details.

nodes.title: LIB: OFFICE SPACES - Abandoned Corporate Ruin

Piles of discarded paperwork are scattered across a water-damaged carpet. Post-apocalyptic, eerie lighting, urban decay, high detail.

nodes.title: LIB: OFFICE SPACES - Zen Minimalist Home Office

nodes.title: LIB: OUTDOOR NATURE - Ancient Mossy Rainforest
widgets_values: Deep inside a primeval rainforest where sunlight filters through a dense canopy in sharp god-rays. Ancient trees with massive gnarled roots are draped in thick emerald moss and hanging vines. A gentle mist clings to the forest floor where bioluminescent mushrooms glow faintly. High dynamic range, cinematic lighting, lush vegetation, 8k resolution.

nodes.title: LIB: OUTDOOR NATURE - Arid Red Rock Canyon
widgets_values: A vast panoramic view of a winding red rock canyon at high noon. The sandstone walls show intricate sedimentary layers and wind-eroded textures. Sparse desert scrub and twisted juniper trees cling to the cliffs. The sky is a piercing turquoise blue with no clouds. Harsh shadows, sharp details, geological realism, wide angle lens.

nodes.title: LIB: OUTDOOR NATURE - Arctic Tundra at Twilight
widgets_values: A desolate and beautiful arctic landscape during the blue hour. Pristine white snow dunes ripple under a frozen wind. In the distance, jagged icy mountains are silhouetted against a sky painted with streaks of aurora borealis. Crystalized ice structures sparkle in the foreground. Ethereal atmosphere, cool color palette, long exposure.

nodes.title: LIB: OUTDOOR NATURE - Alpine Wildflower Meadow
widgets_values: A vibrant sub-alpine meadow in full bloom during mid-summer. Thousands of lupines and paintbrushes create a sea of color. A crystal-clear glacial stream meanders through the field. In the background, snow-capped granite peaks pierce the clouds. Sharp focus, natural sunlight, macro-detail on flowers, breath-taking scenery.

nodes.title: LIB: OUTDOOR NATURE - Stormy Coastal Cliffs
widgets_values: Dark basalt cliffs overlooking a churning grey ocean under a heavy storm sky. Massive waves crash against the rocks sending white sea spray high into the air. A lonely stone lighthouse stands resilient on the precipice. Moody lighting, dramatic atmosphere, wet rock textures, motion blur on water.

nodes.title: LIB: OUTDOOR NATURE - Golden Wheat Field
widgets_values: An endless sea of ripe golden wheat swaying in a gentle breeze. A single weathered oak tree stands in the center of the frame. The horizon is low, giving way to a massive sky filled with towering cumulus clouds. Warm afternoon sun, rural nostalgia, hyper-realistic textures, 35mm film aesthetic.

nodes.title: LIB: OUTDOOR NATURE - Volcanic Obsidian Plain
widgets_values: A stark landscape of black volcanic glass and cooling lava flows. Steam vents rise from deep cracks in the earth. The sky is choked with ash and a dim red sun. Sharp obsidian shards reflect a hellish orange glow from distant magma. Dark fantasy aesthetic, high contrast, gritty texture.

nodes.title: LIB: OUTDOOR NATURE - Autumn Lakeside
widgets_values: A tranquil lake reflecting a forest of maple and birch trees in peak autumn colors of crimson and gold. A thin layer of morning fog rests on the water's surface. A small wooden pier extends into the still water. Soft morning light, peaceful mood, mirror-like reflections, 4k detail.

nodes.title: LIB: SCI-FI & FANTASY - Alien Crystal Forest

nodes.title: LIB: SCI-FI & FANTASY - Dwarven Forge Deep Underground

nodes.title: LIB: SCI-FI & FANTASY - Spaceship Observation Deck
widgets_values: A curved glass window looking out into a swirling colorful nebula and a distant star field. The interior is sleek and dark with glowing control panels. High-tech futuristic chairs. Cinematic space art, deep blacks, vivid purples and blues.

nodes.title: LIB: SCI-FI & FANTASY - The Floating Isles of Zephyr
